title: Shorty's - Fulfill the Dream (1998).mpg
description: Shortys Fulfill the Dream DVD: A true modern skate classic. Shorty's Fulfill the Dream inspired today's generation of rippers. The level and style in this video took the industry by storm, and forever changed it. Featuring modern day legends: Chad Muska, Steve Olson, Peter Smolik, Sammy Baptista, Toan Nguyen, Jesse Silvey, Aaron Snyder, and Brandon Turner. Winner of TWS Best Video 1998, Best Team 1998, Best Street Skater (Chad Muska) 1998, Best Style (Peter Smolik) 1998, and Best Team 1999. Approx 45 minutes
